reviewText: I like the fact that we are able to get more than one movie at a time!
My daughter loved this Christmas gift!

Very nice set. Comes with UltraViolet digital redemption code for all 5 films. Each film is widescreen format and each film is on its own one sided disc. Not much for special features but picture quality is good. Would make a great gift for someone who doesn't have these 5 films.
